<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="T" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Trot1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Trot,</orth> subst. a decrepit old woman: <cit><quote>an old t. with ne'er a tooth in her head,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 1.2.80" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. I, 2, 80</bibl></cit>. Lucio calls Pompey so: <bibl n="shak. mm 3.2.53" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. III, 2, 53</bibl>.
